4. உரிச்சொல்  
adjectives and adverbs. other specifications are included  
as இயற்சொல். common words; திரிசொல்  
learned words; திசைச்சொல்  
provincial words  
or accord ing to the நன்னூல்  
words peculiar to or derived from any of the tamil provinces around the madura district  
or form any of the indian cognate languages; வடசொல் or வடமொழி  
words of sanscrit origin. அவனுடையபேச்சு காற்சொல்லுமரைச்சொல்லும். he speaks broken language; (lit.) half and quarter words. அப்படிச்சொல்லு. say soas a command; or as meaningthat is right  
